&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a passionate and experienced &lt;strong&gt;Engineering Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing team and play a pivotal role in building our Integrations Platform. You will own the systems that connect our platform with external partners, data sources, and internal services - enabling seamless, secure, and scalable data exchange.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead the design and development of integration architecture, including robust APIs, data pipelines, and partner integrations, while helping guide technical direction in collaboration with senior engineers and cross-functional stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
