&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Forward Deployed Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;at Frontera, you’ll own the technical success of our most important clinic implementations and ongoing customer optimizations. You are both a builder and a technical owner in the field - responsible for making complex customer environments work seamlessly with the Frontera platform.&lt;/p&gt;
