&lt;li&gt;Analyze performance across Frontera’s healthcare services, technology, direct-to-parent, and commercial partnership models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate financial and operational data into clear insights for leaders across Operations, Product, Commercial, and Clinical teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support budgeting, forecasting, headcount planning, margin analysis, pricing analysis, and ROI analysis for strategic initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
